0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Robert-De-Niro-birthday-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Robert-De-Niro-birthday-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Robert-De-Niro-birthday-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-de-niro">罗伯特·德尼罗 (Robert De Niro)</a>与好莱坞一些大腕一起庆祝了自己的 80 岁生日，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥 (Leonardo DiCaprio)</a>和长期合作者马丁·斯科塞斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">Martin Scorsese)</a> 。</p><p>周四（8 月 17 日），这位演员在纽约与家人和密友共进了一场特别的晚宴，庆祝了这一具有里程碑意义的生日，其中包括他的女友蒂芙尼·陈（Tiffany Chen），<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-many-children-does-robert-de-niro-have-3444275">他最近迎来了他的第七个孩子</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">《花月杀手》评论：马丁·斯科塞斯令人心碎的真实犯罪冷门</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://people.com/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese-tiffany-chen-and-more-gather-to-celebrate-robert-de-niros-80th-birthday-7692759" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>报道，晚宴在翠贝卡格林威治酒店的 Locanda Verde 意大利餐厅举行，该餐厅由德尼罗拥有。</p><p>其他出席者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>和他的妻子南希·谢维尔、 <em>《教父》</em>导演弗朗西斯·福特·科波拉、<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars">星球大战</a>创始人乔治·卢卡斯和克里斯托弗·沃肯。您可以查看下面的一些图片。 </p><figure id="attachment_3486087" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3486087" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3486087" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro.jpg" alt="保罗·麦卡特尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Paul-McCartney-robert-de-niro-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3486087" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 在纽约参加罗伯特·德尼罗 (Robert De Niro) 的 80 岁生日。图片来源：Gotham/GC Images </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3486089" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3486089" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3486089" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party.jpg" alt="马丁斯科塞斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Martin-Scorsese-de-niro-party-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3486089" class="wp-caption-text">马丁·斯科塞斯在纽约参加罗伯特·德尼罗的生日。图片来源：Gotham/GC Images</figcaption></figure><p>纽约州前州长安德鲁·科莫、大卫·布莱恩、贝蒂·米德勒和简·克拉科斯基也出席了会议。</p><p>与德尼罗一起主演<em>《好家伙》的</em>黛比·玛扎在 Instagram 上分享了一张照片来庆祝自己的生日。 “鲍勃生日快乐！祝您80岁快乐！非常爱你和家人！今晚玩得开心！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwDDFgOI0YG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm